[l] In einem seltenen Moment der Klarheit aeussert sich der franzoesische Aussenminister zur Ernennung von Boris Johnson:In Boris Johnson, Britain has appointed a liar with his back against the wall as its new foreign secretary at a time when somebody reliable is needed in the role, his French counterpart Jean-Marc Ayrault said on Thursday.Da war wohl der Zensor pinkeln.
